[{"id":7379,"date":"2022-04-13T18:20:57","modified":"2022-06-08T20:47:04","slug":"help-how-to-get-toolkits","link":"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/help-how-to-get-toolkits\/","title":{"rendered":"HELP!\u200aHow to get\u00a0Toolkits?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"graf graf--p\">At the moment of writing, many Star Atlas enthusiasts are struggling with the Solana network, in particular when trying to acquire Toolkits to sustain their fleet.<\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">Nine out of ten times (if not far more often) your Toolkit-purchase transaction will fail. This has to do with the current\u200a\u2014\u200ainsane\u200a\u2014\u200alevels of <a class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/staratlas\/status\/1514254318500663302?s=21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/staratlas\/status\/1514254318500663302?s=21\">bot activity<\/a> on the Solana network.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"graf graf--h3\">Solution?<\/h3>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">There is no solution to this issue, but there is a way that might increase your chance of success by quite a bit. How? By temporarily using a different marketplace, like Raydium.<\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">This has the following benefits:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"postList\">\n<li class=\"graf graf--li\">The chance of your transaction failing appears to be smaller (but it will fail plenty of times still)<\/li>\n<li class=\"graf graf--li\">Failure goes quicker, so you can try again faster<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"graf graf--h3\">Using Raydium<\/h3>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">How to do this? Follow these steps:<\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 Copy the <em class=\"markup--em markup--p-em\">Market ID<\/em> for the Toolkits here:<br \/>\n<strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">32Pr4MhSD1K4J9buESjjbSZnXWLQ5oHFgB9MhEC2hp6J<\/strong><\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"graf graf--blockquote\"><p><em class=\"markup--em markup--blockquote-em\">\u00a0Or, if you don\u2019t trust this:<br \/>\n&#8211; Go to the <\/em><a class=\"markup--anchor markup--blockquote-anchor\" href=\"https:\/\/play.staratlas.com\/market\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https:\/\/play.staratlas.com\/market\"><em class=\"markup--em markup--blockquote-em\">Star Atlas marketplace<\/em><\/a><em class=\"markup--em markup--blockquote-em\"><br \/>\n&#8211; Navigate to the Toolkit page<br \/>\n&#8211; Copy the <\/em>Market ID<em class=\"markup--em markup--blockquote-em\"> portion (the long hash with letter and numbers) from the URL<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*_PYeX70pZiOXkf-bMdvYaA.png\" data-image-id=\"1*_PYeX70pZiOXkf-bMdvYaA.png\" data-width=\"1736\" data-height=\"1228\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Star Atlas\u200a\u2014\u200aIf you want to copy the market ID\u00a0yourself<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">2\ufe0f\u20e3 Next, navigate to <a class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" href=\"https:\/\/dex.raydium.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https:\/\/dex.raydium.io\/\">Raydium<\/a> (<a class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" href=\"https:\/\/dex.raydium.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-href=\"https:\/\/dex.raydium.io\/\">https:\/\/dex.raydium.io\/<\/a>) and connect your wallet (do not forget this step, else Raydium might get stuck in a loop near the end)<\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">3\ufe0f\u20e3 Click the small \u201c+\u201d in the blue circle near the top-left corner of the page<\/p>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*bM2A_LKTcvpWBf8IvNLsrw.png\" data-image-id=\"1*bM2A_LKTcvpWBf8IvNLsrw.png\" data-width=\"908\" data-height=\"376\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Raydium\u200a\u2014\u200aAdd a new\u00a0market<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">4\ufe0f\u20e3 Paste the <em class=\"markup--em markup--p-em\">Market ID<\/em> into the first input box, and add something that makes sense to you into the other two inputs, like \u201cToolkit\u201d. If you get an &#8220;Invalid market ID&#8221; notification, make sure you did not include any spaces.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*hDLx4rNnte3zH54GLa_dtg.png\" data-image-id=\"1*hDLx4rNnte3zH54GLa_dtg.png\" data-width=\"1090\" data-height=\"656\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Raydium\u200a\u2014\u200aAdd a new market for\u00a0Toolkits<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">5\ufe0f\u20e3 Navigate to the newly added marketplace by clicking on the current market in the top left corner and selecting \u201cTOOOOOOOL\/ATLAS\u201d (or the name you gave the market in the previous step).<br \/>\n<em><strong>Note:<\/strong><\/em> Instead of the &#8220;RAY\/USDC&#8221; that you see in this screenshot, you will probably see a different market listed here, or &#8220;<strong>Select market<\/strong>&#8221; if you&#8217;ve never been here before.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*3Ypsm8R3R7YdmaIhxQS2bA.png\" data-image-id=\"1*3Ypsm8R3R7YdmaIhxQS2bA.png\" data-width=\"928\" data-height=\"328\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Raydium\u200a\u2014\u200aSelect the newly added\u00a0market<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">6\ufe0f\u20e3 Now you are going to create a standard limit order, by inputting the price you are willing to pay per Toolkit into the \u201cLimit price\u201d. This is of course equal to the price asked by Star Atlas, which you can find on their marketplace page. For convenience, you can copy it here:<br \/>\n<strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">0.0017408<\/strong><\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">7\ufe0f\u20e3 Enter the amount you want in the \u201cAmount\u201d input. If you can afford it, it would make sense to select enough so that you don\u2019t have to come back for the next 2 to 3 days at the least.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*hAV7TuTXNn6s-_qMxmXSLA.png\" data-image-id=\"1*hAV7TuTXNn6s-_qMxmXSLA.png\" data-width=\"768\" data-height=\"1196\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Raydium\u200a\u2014\u200aFill in your order with the official price and amount\u00a0required<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">8\ufe0f\u20e3 Now, leave \u201cTotal\u201d alone -it should have calculated the correct amount of ATLAS you will have to pay- and click the \u201cLIMIT BUY Toolkit\u201d button.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"graf graf--blockquote\"><p><em class=\"markup--em markup--blockquote-em\">There is a good chance this results in an error, but you can do it multiple times relatively quickly. Usually sooner or later one goes through. Once it does, carry on!<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">9\ufe0f\u20e3 Go to your <a class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" href=\"https:\/\/play.staratlas.com\/inventory?category=resource\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https:\/\/play.staratlas.com\/inventory?category=resource\">inventory<\/a> on the Star Atlas website and claim your toolkits.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"graf graf--figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"graf-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn-images-1.medium.com\/max\/1600\/1*Z3WXUv8Ai7CiduUpDnifLw.png\" data-image-id=\"1*Z3WXUv8Ai7CiduUpDnifLw.png\" data-width=\"392\" data-height=\"790\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><figcaption class=\"imageCaption\">Sat Atlas\u200a\u2014\u200aAs some ATLAS was used for fees, the amount is less than\u00a0ordered<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">\u26a0\ufe0f <strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\"><em class=\"markup--em markup--p-em\">Note:<\/em><\/strong> You will have <strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">received fewer<\/strong> toolkits than you ordered. This is normal, as there are some fees that are not automatically taken into account when the \u201cTotal\u201d was calculated for you by Raydium.<\/p>\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">Again: This is normal, as a portion of your ATLAS was used to pay for fees.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"graf graf--pullquote\"><p><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--pullquote-strong\">Good luck!<\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>At the moment of writing, many Star Atlas enthusiasts are struggling with the Solana network, in particular when trying to acquire Toolkits to sustain their fleet. Nine out of ten times (if not far more often) your Toolkit-purchase transaction will fail. This has to do with the current\u200a\u2014\u200ainsane\u200a\u2014\u200alevels of bot activity on the Solana network. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1}]